{"tid":550110,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"廢青鳩遊日記（杜拜英國法比荷）","createTime":"2018-02-04T11:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T12:33:17.000Z","uid":141782,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8ef2a14770722ce90b1fe85b837fc6b8ba4f9b5b","tid":550110,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:55:01.000Z","msg":"由於今個sem 返三日放十日實在太得閒，所以好多時間搭火車周圍鳩fing，本身想淨係打英國，不過諗住整多幾個番外篇打埋我長假去邊度fing<br />\n自己覺得同舊年比自己越黎越識plan行程搵著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n杜拜--&gt;英國<br />\n<br />\n未去過杜拜，之前轉機經過杜拜已經好想去，發誓要拿拿臨去<br />\n結果今次就喺杜拜加阿布扎比停三日<br />\n我on99以為book 咗A380，一入到去頂book錯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩隔離冇人，唔係坐咁耐好唔安落<br />\n平時一條友我實單邊位，不過今程機太爆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/192617_717c9dbc7fc5897fb0fa532c0d33a321.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F192617_717c9dbc7fc5897fb0fa532c0d33a321.JPG&h=6d5ecb77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杜拜機場大就大，d 裝修都幾柒下，同我之前諗會好華麗完全唔同<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/192834_f65afcf46308e31b0612e59f60ebf228.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F192834_f65afcf46308e31b0612e59f60ebf228.JPG&h=f798569f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出發前見到信用卡有免費transfer， 即刻book，佢話一粒鐘等候時間，過咗鐘就罰六百晚，心諗一粒鐘實冇死啦，過關拎行李都係第一個，十五分鐘出到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，等sim卡嗰度本身我排第二，去到前面個印度人突然成家親戚十條友衝出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，整咗9個字都有，望住隻錶個司機又係咁sms 催我，急到尿都標埋出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後順利上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/193501_1378fde2dcaecf6d5b4d0da3fdabcc5f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F193501_1378fde2dcaecf6d5b4d0da3fdabcc5f.JPG&h=c3f0bce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次住嘅係我小學嗰陣睇向世界出發夏雨搭船嗰間運河酒店（當年我已經下定決心要住呢間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），間酒店係三間夾埋一齊，我嗰間係villa （Al Qasr at Madinat Jumeirah）<br />\n<br />\n保安嚴密check晒booking details先比入<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/193947_be9268ca67123fc66059bda69b3ea54c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F193947_be9268ca67123fc66059bda69b3ea54c.JPG&h=a8d8905d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/193954_3f85a369e904b1113953bd0c5813091e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F193954_3f85a369e904b1113953bd0c5813091e.JPG&h=ee6cd7d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入到villa入面仲有大堂，有私人管家幫book船book車<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/194453_c7a609e8d6e10079571cf0175ed5cff0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F194453_c7a609e8d6e10079571cf0175ed5cff0.png&h=fe70780e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身book最cheap 嗰間房，冇記錯book嗰陣四千頭一晚<br />\n佢可能見我話想要河景upgrade 比我，check 下要六千蚊晚，開心到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/193844_006cec997061fd23603210c174b1fc35.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F193844_006cec997061fd23603210c174b1fc35.JPG&h=a716a4c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/194602_f03bc33e5e30e5fd46ea600c9d0d5c3c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F194602_f03bc33e5e30e5fd46ea600c9d0d5c3c.JPG&h=e5babf50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擺低野拿拿臨沖去沙灘，一出去41度熱撚到呢，不過隻熱法同香港唔同，佢隻熱係辣肉但乾，唔會透唔到氣，相反香港係濕到氣都透唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n波斯灣呀屌，聽就聽過波斯灣戰爭，估唔到依家成個波斯灣我獨霸（冇人）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/195301_e31540e2dee5ff3abfeefa4ebc911776.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F195301_e31540e2dee5ff3abfeefa4ebc911776.png&h=b21903c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/195307_86d5f67a02044604a84f09603ab12150.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F195307_86d5f67a02044604a84f09603ab12150.png&h=275c656e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為熱到仆街既關係，我都係去咗dubai mall<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手下留情唔好起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dcc225b9817d9ba286261a8e8e289870595e83c","tid":550110,"uid":141782,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T12:12:27.000Z","msg":"管家幫我叫左架的士去dubai mall，我啱啱落機邊得黎咁多散紙，的士費唔幾得幾錢，不過起碼要找八十蚊到，跟住條友話no change no change，我頂你個肺吖，後尾揾搵下又真係比我揾到張散紙，都蝕成十幾蚊比佢（有d 巴打話杜拜的士係唔找錢，，事實證明次次返酒店有職員𥄫實嗰程係會找既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n物價比我想像平，同香港差唔多，百零蚊到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/200118_d681c26f9029eda0bd6f201b706a6aec.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F200118_d681c26f9029eda0bd6f201b706a6aec.JPG&h=0a6b0bcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個mall 同香港d shops 差不多咩都冇買<br />\n<br />\n第二日搭地鐵去Bastakiya, 好多藝術野有博物館咁<br />\n<br />\n地鐵有女性專用車廂，有條鬼佬行咗入去班女人好似發現炸彈咁<br />\n地鐵都幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/200946_d56e2097792dac0a3f4410e13bbc8b53.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F200946_d56e2097792dac0a3f4410e13bbc8b53.JPG&h=788bffe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/201111_5bce8c7929d43f5ebfb1d5a969c73d90.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F201111_5bce8c7929d43f5ebfb1d5a969c73d90.png&h=8a589afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/201136_423f0c7011a038e03e56278c0cba2178.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F201136_423f0c7011a038e03e56278c0cba2178.JPG&h=6376d04f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/201141_eb3f798505d065a3b89ab65debf1c32b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F201141_eb3f798505d065a3b89ab65debf1c32b.JPG&h=d3d8315b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f4c02289afbf12eb821f0721ba29bcdf5df6505","tid":550110,"uid":141782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T12:26:38.000Z","msg":"Bastakiya嗰頭應該係窮撚既世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多窮既外勞，d街又舊，好多印度勞工<br />\n聽咁多印度佬新聞既我拿拿臨火箭速度行，事實係自己嚇自己<br />\n去到迴旋處d 車快到我唔識過，有個印度佬見我on99企喺度幾分鐘，就過黎話同我過去，過完馬路佢就走咗<br />\n<br />\n街景<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/201749_1db264e61bf69cf12cc18681748196d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F201749_1db264e61bf69cf12cc18681748196d4.jpg&h=a6603a61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/201910_100d3bf049d00373695553872f266e49.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F201910_100d3bf049d00373695553872f266e49.png&h=8d12367c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/201914_8b5accaeaccf4875ca1ab6023ce346cc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F201914_8b5accaeaccf4875ca1ab6023ce346cc.png&h=04c0faa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去到Bastakia Quarter<br />\n門口有間好靚既餐廳，有陣強烈羶味<br />\n所以我就入咗去<br />\n<br />\n仲以為門口嗰兩隻野係裝飾啫<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/202131_7e60c388e58bb0a9f4bbe3a4aa73d0cc.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F202131_7e60c388e58bb0a9f4bbe3a4aa73d0cc.JPG&h=aba8d7ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/202137_304ca95b933a153c1ff07ce9e3df4530.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F202137_304ca95b933a153c1ff07ce9e3df4530.JPG&h=300714e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/202145_3360e387fef140a92a395f4ab3b4b6d3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F202145_3360e387fef140a92a395f4ab3b4b6d3.JPG&h=a57b8d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一上個menu，屌<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/202250_3be5533588112eba9b83d93bcc1ae98d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F202250_3be5533588112eba9b83d93bcc1ae98d.JPG&h=6515a5ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後叫咗杯野飲算，後尾有一堆大陸大媽入黎，一人整件斑馬漢堡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBastakia Quarter<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/202457_3ecb9217f10cba14a69875a709dbda8f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F202457_3ecb9217f10cba14a69875a709dbda8f.JPG&h=aeaf3794&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/202503_68414dc80c6f77fd710a315fe86b5443.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F202503_68414dc80c6f77fd710a315fe86b5443.JPG&h=7a37812a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbook 咗黃昏上Burj Khalifa睇日落，又返去dubai mall<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/202613_829ab2a6523057bc5b59ee1ff65f794f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F202613_829ab2a6523057bc5b59ee1ff65f794f.jpg&h=f6b9adba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9da8f62c702834d5975cf847ee3bef92e16e243d","tid":550110,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T12:45:54.000Z","msg":"Burj Khalifa 有125/148樓，148樓黃昏飛成千蚊張半身好肉赤，不過人一世物一世冇理由爭幾百唔上最top<br />\n<br />\n148 有priority，可以唔洗排隊，入到去大堂有房等夠鐘有咖啡飲<br />\n杜拜真係乜撚都分階級，business過關有priority，搭地鐵有頭等，連觀景台都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/204102_f277e1ec4ab22e951259b2f8c1616f4f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F204102_f277e1ec4ab22e951259b2f8c1616f4f.png&h=7a23b362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/204106_ac1904b5676085a05e6aa3e5a3214ddf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F204106_ac1904b5676085a05e6aa3e5a3214ddf.