gmoji\" /> <br />\n純白色極奢華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/210150_101044bb9941183f91defd2581e06a29.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F210150_101044bb9941183f91defd2581e06a29.JPG&h=da969289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手造地氈唔斷咁舖晒成個清真寺好震撼<br />\n入到黎就算唔係muslim都會覺得好神聖嗰隻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/210712_37893a59655f94096c7a85781b12df6a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F210712_37893a59655f94096c7a85781b12df6a.png&h=cd4bda01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/210743_a3e5a0e89ee6cd6fea21b05cc427d40c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F210743_a3e5a0e89ee6cd6fea21b05cc427d40c.png&h=a4a1855f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4765bb3339f324d0565147eda3a5b9b5b0fab1f5","tid":550110,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T13:59:41.000Z","msg":"係喎屌唔記得仲有芬蘭挪威dublin 都會喺道打埋<br />\n意大利請移玉步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed57e27d1187485733d67035e2a5defb66ce72f8","tid":550110,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"對杜拜ff 咁耐話咁快就完咗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國<br />\n啱啱喺隔籬post 見到有人話咩英國好撚悶淨係得溝仔溝女同落club真係好唔認同<br />\n一個人性格悶去邊都悶架啦，英國咁撚多野睇都叫悶真係冇野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知點解咁多day off，所以成日走咗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBath<br />\nbath 又唔大所以冇咩plan 過<br />\n一出火車站去咗Roman Baths<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/221815_ae7d75848b2b637d756358f0ad8f0b91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F221815_ae7d75848b2b637d756358f0ad8f0b91.png&h=9c660540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過Bath Abbey<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/221819_e9f5f900f18f3bc2ce4d5c4d0c6b5c65.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F221819_e9f5f900f18f3bc2ce4d5c4d0c6b5c65.png&h=f10b1af0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n靚係靚既不過冇想像咁大，好多人，d 水好大陣味<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/221830_f055558d25f9e127468daafcc715976e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F221830_f055558d25f9e127468daafcc715976e.png&h=4b45c4ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/221833_b4bae39495e495eacb2a2c06ccfde96b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F221833_b4bae39495e495eacb2a2c06ccfde96b.png&h=22e4b5ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過bath 最靚既都係街景<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/222336_84a51c9f5e5c407f00e852b4eca7eaaa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F222336_84a51c9f5e5c407f00e852b4eca7eaaa.png&h=1903e5a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/222341_59430fc5d3137b65acdc2856772cda6a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F222341_59430fc5d3137b65acdc2856772cda6a.png&h=22e4be9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPulteney Bridge<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/222516_400ef18f4a64c9ba4e38eb41ba5bf11b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F222516_400ef18f4a64c9ba4e38eb41ba5bf11b.png&h=a2fd1022&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba96a59856ef439db3b1dfcf3fd37b6c31d18b61","tid":550110,"uid":136299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:58:19.000Z","msg":"lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc0e04a56c0dd106721fac9a3297f63fe292790","tid":550110,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T21:11:16.000Z","msg":"Edinburgh&amp; Glasgow<br />\n<br />\n去scotland 嗰陣撞正新年<br />\nEdinburgh日頭真係周圍都好靚，不過一夜晚又冬又落雨嗰陣硬係好似有鬼咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺酒店行出去行行下唔知去撚咗邊，搭的士返royal mile，四分鐘都冇成十鎊<br />\n個的士司機話新年個價唔同，叫我帶多d 前入Christmas market<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/044911_a4812dc9c98b62817dd3dd2ef1e53b41.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F044911_a4812dc9c98b62817dd3dd2ef1e53b41.JPG&h=cce1494f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/044921_8a59c017389814c59f459c70a81fc929.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F044921_8a59c017389814c59f459c70a81fc929.JPG&h=ee5766ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/044925_23a8ee126dc58304df144430d9b6cec1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F044925_23a8ee126dc58304df144430d9b6cec1.JPG&h=61b3272c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nraclette真係好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/045213_ed18f4d1fa5fa04dc52feeac25c8d010.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F045213_ed18f4d1fa5fa04dc52feeac25c8d010.JPG&h=8ced74a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去完market出黎差唔多日落，見到個天咁靚即刻走上去Calton Hill<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/044928_55090c47b277ce6e7eac2e1853d76e85.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F044928_55090c47b277ce6e7eac2e1853d76e85.JPG&h=b7111dd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/045354_258dc3fbecf7aae41dde4b89f480e81a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F045354_258dc3fbecf7aae41dde4b89f480e81a.JPG&h=c8febb8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二朝話晒細個都係harry potter fans 就去咩elephant 朝聖下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/045540_f7f4064224297feecb04f51955a1106c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F045540_f7f4064224297feecb04f51955a1106c.JPG&h=53313f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/045546_9bba1388733ba8362c12927d24c1c910.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F045546_9bba1388733ba8362c12927d24c1c910.JPG&h=1f680da9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/045554_9952e33ee47b80f4b5e7f829d3ebe37a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F045554_9952e33ee47b80f4b5e7f829d3ebe37a.JPG&h=0c304e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝修都好多elephant<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/045600_cf628499f4eebd0fd72367142c4f8b31.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F045600_cf628499f4eebd0fd72367142c4f8b31.JPG&h=a3b289a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再喺附近兜下，呢條victoria street嗰日一條友揪住30kg 行斜路行到有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/045905_1ee7f1aca7737f0c886e9149e6a3af09.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F045905_1ee7f1aca7737f0c886e9149e6a3af09.JPG&h=cb945444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/045946_ca67da0771c76ec49f151d196c2c21a6.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F045946_ca67da0771c76ec49f151d196c2c21a6.JPG&h=3c5e7f6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個castle 唔多想比錢入，不過最後都係入咗<br />\n淨係記得試飲咗杯Whisky 好飲到依家都念念不忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/050226_f68a9d55a163e926f6a02e5de5e2654c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F050226_f68a9d55a163e926f6a02e5de5e2654c.JPG&h=c09127ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後嗰日報咗rabbie 去highlands<br />\n不過我唔夠時間淨係去到一日，第日一定會再去<br />\nHighlands d 天氣好cls，呢頭有太陽五分鐘大風大雨落埋雹<br />\n呢d tour 有時都幾好，好多highlands 故仔聽<br />\n個tour guide 講到好傳神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/050828_b52b3ae74063e3a190224dbd9b96952c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F050828_b52b3ae74063e3a190224dbd9b96952c.png&h=56f09299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/050704_1a1d93300492e97b00469bd6a1a09b57.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F050704_1a1d93300492e97b00469bd6a1a09b57.JPG&h=ca90ac38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高地牛個樣好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/050711_236fa88f167ed407bfbf44307ad0049f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F050711_236fa88f167ed407bfbf44307ad0049f.JPG&h=cc1d0455&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/050717_2ea4dba9955de856b94ac75111e1f786.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F050717_2ea4dba9955de856b94ac75111e1f786.JPG&h=e18b7d5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"086b8cae5f337e8f66dfe76549f30de1dcebc6f2","tid":550110,"uid":141782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T22:12:56.000Z","msg":"之後嗰日答去Glasgow，之前highlands個tour guide 話glasgow d人好熱情都真係名不虛傳<br />\n明明車程一粒鐘都唔洗，d 口音變化可以咁大<br />\n我英文都叫幾好啦起碼睇戲冇字幕都聽到九成九<br />\n去到Glasgow我一隻字都聽唔明<br />\n個waiter同我講野完全唔知佢噏乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nglasgow uni<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/060458_241d550029ddd65a25581d4a2a117803.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F060458_241d550029ddd65a25581d4a2a117803.JPG&h=1c75f5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKelvingrove Art Gallery and Museum<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/060843_3a0335ddaad69cd2ac367ff517037a12.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F060843_3a0335ddaad69cd2ac367ff517037a12.JPG&h=8ad1f8c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/060849_51d009e77e09c6ead7df363008ee8e9d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F060849_51d009e77e09c6ead7df363008ee8e9d.JPG&h=6c14b308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去旅行越黎越唔鍾意搭車，行到盡量行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好hea<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/061019_bf5915b101170546565f2add5a1970e0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F061019_bf5915b101170546565f2add5a1970e0.JPG&h=45f5c2cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/061024_5459811e2f9372c1dc47659c33463766.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F061024_5459811e2f9372c1dc47659c33463766.JPG&h=13bb43b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/061030_34caafe82e48861e0df3174083983de2.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F061030_34caafe82e48861e0df3174083983de2.JPG&h=482ec546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n撩下佢叫佢過黎，佢爬埋上我度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後尾望真d我唔係樹佢就走撚咗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/061237_811acc53cde28549b8704fd0ee6622e2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F061237_811acc53cde28549b8704fd0ee6622e2.png&h=f65c13ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb7afcd16f805803b8085429148c97fa68ff3cc2","tid":550110,"uid":41096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T22:27:12.000Z","msg":"英國讀書撚LM"},{"pid":"334a8987a140db9503f9a2cb2d05f34a486f96d7","tid":550110,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T22:49:28.000Z","msg":"打返個瑞士番外篇先<br />\n近兩年去咗兩次瑞士一次夏天一次冬天（四月又會去多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n瑞士都算最無敵嗰隻，自然環境城市旅遊乜野都世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以唔知去邊好想去旅行既人我首推瑞士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n滑雪係我最鍾意既運動，一冬天會身痕好想滑<br />\n今次係zurich去zermatt<br />\n<br />\n呢邊係gornergrat我唔係呢邊滑，純粹睇下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/063257_4138f3e9b923ff28cfbba0bb92900b66.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F063257_4138f3e9b923ff28cfbba0bb92900b66.JPG&h=fc4db349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/063302_60c4cff3c3ff2fad14a34e6d1c0edd46.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F063302_60c4cff3c3ff2fad14a34e6d1c0edd46.JPG&h=3fe57fb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/063313_8861e4e692ed5d7799cdec0ced007baf.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F063313_8861e4e692ed5d7799cdec0ced007baf.JPG&h=df34142e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/063320_6997a7f2c54000b8975a13f90fdc7724.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F063320_6997a7f2c54000b8975a13f90fdc7724.JPG&h=4cf0077d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nmatterhorn唔夠雪有d 可惜<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/063324_8e2eaeec58f5305290ac24a424f34a46.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F063324_8e2eaeec58f5305290ac24a424f34a46.JPG&h=91a649e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落山嗰陣，想去Stellisee行下<br />\n車站職員同我講結晒冰會仆死行唔到<br />\n見到勁多人照行，我一心諗住黎到梗係要行啦，照行，成條路結嘥冰，我就好似坐雪兜咁（不過冇雪兜）用個蘿柚跣落山啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爬返上去都成粒鐘，爬到日落先上返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/064840_8cfdd0f80b2685ab2806b2f4e58f8435.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F064840_8cfdd0f80b2685ab2806b2f4e58f8435.JPG&h=f3bd10fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後果日去matterhorn glacier paradise滑<br />\non99冇帶雪鏡，點知冇得租（以前去過好多場都有）<br />\n不過太陽好猛冇辦法，買咗個最平既都要千六蚊<br />\n貴到牙都痛埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nZermatt 入面，著住成套野搬住套ski 行到on99去paradise，行到去先發覺有車搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/063949_9836b533397eea1d9516750881ed669c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F063949_9836b533397eea1d9516750881ed669c.JPG&h=7c979d52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/063955_bde5463fe87f0c007c17fe581be716a2.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F063955_bde5463fe87f0c007c17fe581be716a2.JPG&h=d5ead4a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐洲最高cable car，唔滑可以上去觀景<br />\n我就滑過意大利cervinia <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/064003_3189690ce8cf61f8f5d974106edb6beb.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F064003_3189690ce8cf61f8f5d974106edb6beb.JPG&h=80650b27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/064009_ad43e39d3110763ae69747da8bef620d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F064009_ad43e39d3110763ae69747da8bef620d.JPG&h=1f1198a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返到落山都夜晚lu<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/064335_b2d40938bcafc0b3efcf50930b4e4c5e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F064335_b2d40938bcafc0b3efcf50930b4e4c5e.JPG&h=2feae61c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/064340_ddf1e2c98750d9b93476854edf6b340e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F064340_ddf1e2c98750d9b93476854edf6b340e.JPG&h=03ec0be6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33b13b090e2fb14b745b30de0c52699a53d58265","tid":550110,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T23:24:00.000Z","msg":"有個post 我推zurich係咁比人負評<br />\n明明zurich 就好撚正<br />\ncity 入面街景靚唔在講<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/071252_b71153920994ff0caeeb10899b9292df.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F071252_b71153920994ff0caeeb10899b9292df.png&h=c76fdc33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/071256_6e634f56b35a406c14b8bdd9a1db25dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F071256_6e634f56b35a406c14b8bdd9a1db25dd.png&h=28bfed14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近近地可以去Uetliberg睇晒zurich 全景<br />\n當然有d 人會覺得瑞士咁多山洗鬼黎呢個<br />\n但係呢個山咁啱我去有winter inversion 好靚好似仙景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搭train上Uetliberg<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/071538_443b1e923c7c3e696ca301f43c58708a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F071538_443b1e923c7c3e696ca301f43c58708a.JPG&h=501e23cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/071643_c4bd2ff44669791186c337b430b5f84e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F071643_c4bd2ff44669791186c337b430b5f84e.png&h=1d2dd7ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/071656_7d1b46573a6f14bf68e28cdaf1759abb.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F071656_7d1b46573a6f14bf68e28cdaf1759abb.JPG&h=1818e5a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行到條鎖橋，洗唔洗咁大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/072222_1ea829c93df283ff424e188db42c25ce.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F072222_1ea829c93df283ff424e188db42c25ce.JPG&h=dd04c234&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中央車站<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/072253_a660d2f1686b98584cd2c10d3fbc8a52.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F072253_a660d2f1686b98584cd2c10d3fbc8a52.JPG&h=dd4f6b8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘇黎世真係好有錢，成街名車都算，最緊要係同d杜拜土豪唔同<br />\n喺酒店tea 完行出黎嗰d 真係成個貴婦咁，唔似杜拜佬咁俗<br />\n總之成個city d人都係斯斯文文硬係好高貴,有錢得黎內斂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (雖然日內瓦都係)"},{"pid":"363fed77a48aa485fd25cf685861871ac4a20261","tid":550110,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T16:35:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2f92f3b2a2fabc2050b771736695133d27dee6cd","tid":550110,"uid":88