":"英法比荷"},{"pid":"b5c3d19675a811c79388c150a89a5d16a7e2c994","tid":550110,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0249036b7448df734621111aa74be4f352854a76","tid":550110,"uid":88301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9071c5e10e65e7dace56602fd4c1a9f0526c8d23","tid":550110,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f92f3b2a2fabc2050b771736695133d27dee6cd","tid":550110,"uid":88301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T04:26:45.000Z","msg":"正啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟都諗住五月獨遊，愛丁堡入之後一路南下，再去荷蘭德國最後蘇黎世走<br />\n<br />\n巴打去咗幾多日？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"你講邊度去幾多日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔係連續去架<br />\n不過夾埋澳紐嗰d都成一年幾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T08:46:46.000Z","msg":"英法比荷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T11:34:56.000Z","msg":"英國讀書，平時多數1-3 日去其他地方<br />\n法 冬天4 日, 黎緊春天去多次五日<br />\n荷 春天6 日 冬天4 日<br />\n比  3 日<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404cdcdb65212b5fd3d09cd5b3e3bcefdf3a2ea0","tid":550110,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T12:33:17.000Z","msg":"有人睇咁我繼續打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上上下堂好想行開下，見到brighton 好似天氣冇落雨就book weekend 去<br />\n都知brighton大風架啦，但係冇諗過大風到咁，同埋好濕所以溫度唔低（～2度）都凍到頭暈<br />\n<br />\nBrighton Pier 好懷舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/195258_422292758c976c6893efe96f6e9ac0c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F195258_422292758c976c6893efe96f6e9ac0c0.jpg&h=d5575e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺碼頭隔離求其食<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/195409_ce41e5acfe4ee263b8ef471cfca01886.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F195409_ce41e5acfe4ee263b8ef471cfca01886.JPG&h=f193645d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行行下又落大雨所以入去royal pavilion順便睇下<br />\n喺歐洲好少見呢種印度建築，入面裝修係中國+西方特色<br />\n好值得入去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/200141_b7f2a0a4bcf96453d7a3b3b873ac67f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F200141_b7f2a0a4bcf96453d7a3b3b873ac67f6.jpg&h=94bb0d73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官網圖片: <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/200039_d4739b1d95eaa59b327cbb07567244b0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F200039_d4739b1d95eaa59b327cbb07567244b0.png&h=04391f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/200046_4436873ee3d67a60abd690383eafd003.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F200046_4436873ee3d67a60abd690383eafd003.png&h=72bdbb65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二朝日出就出發去seven sisters，經過pier好靚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/200323_de24939d678dc0d94e5125d4712a3b8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F200323_de24939d678dc0d94e5125d4712a3b8b.jpg&h=a39ddb8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前一晚落完大雨都知大鑊啦，去到全部泥水夾雜狗屎，行每一步都會陷入泥入面，d local 行會著hunter<br />\n我行落d 泥路度行到吱吱聲個阿婆仲話我著錯鞋<br />\n最後唔知點解揩到成條褲都係泥<br />\n不過呢d 景真係心曠神怡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/200743_30423940959e9f659aca58885d309e56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F200743_30423940959e9f659aca58885d309e56.png&h=5737f6f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/201130_6c01dd314aea3dd9f97c93bb697ee9dc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F201130_6c01dd314aea3dd9f97c93bb697ee9dc.png&h=0f85f664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/201205_51fb5fa897c84c17a4c284f081e8bacf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F201205_51fb5fa897c84c17a4c284f081e8bacf.jpg&h=bda0becb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭巴士返出黎，見到windmill落去睇下<br />\n真係乜都冇得草地同windmill，好凍拿拿臨走人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/203023_a87ee289d3cade8749c51927406cbeab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F203023_a87ee289d3cade8749c51927406cbeab.png&h=f949c0f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入到city 諗住去marina，有短插曲<br />\n有條四十幾歲既白人，我係錯巴入近窗位，佢一坐落黎launched at me with force 我一野隊咗埋窗口<br />\n跟住我望佢，佢食緊花生噴一噴氣，噴到我隻手袖係花生碎<br />\n於是我被triggered，一野推開佢行出走廊位，然後鬧：<br />\n&quot;做乜撚野呀屌你老母啦，你條撚樣，我報警你assault我，咪撚旨意走得甩&quot;<br />\n<br />\n跟住就叫司機報警，後尾司機直接車咗我地去警察局<br />\n開頭我都奇怪佢零反應，後門門開住都唔走，巴士司機叫我地行佢又真係跟住入警察局<br />\n落完一大輪口供，警察話呢個人成日捉入黎，唔係因為佢係壞人，係因為佢得十歲智商<br />\n咁最後發現佢係低B既我都下咗啖氣<br />\n差館出黎繼續搭車去marina<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/202553_4ce2e72480550772fc9763b8b98bba02.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F202553_4ce2e72480550772fc9763b8b98bba02.JPG&h=f5ee23d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二朝，第一次食breakfast club，行陣街就搭車返屋企<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/202614_3d4949aebb3cf96b1e3f6ca6b348e438.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F202614_3d4949aebb3cf96b1e3f6ca6b348e438.JPG&h=52473a4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/203152_af892d2fe295567b96b65e2986717315.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F203152_af892d2fe295567b96b65e2986717315.png&h=b40f0160&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/203157_64658334d9081d776e17ee4a37f72a06.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F203157_64658334d9081d776e17ee4a37f72a06.png&h=33da646f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/203202_97946da2e11937874c8980d23f64cd56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F203202_97946da2e11937874c8980d23f64cd56.png&h=9969b045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nweekend hea 住完咗"}]}